    <!-- Application Structure Plan:
         This Single Page Application (SPA) transforms the static "Local Service Demand Survey" into a dynamic "Demand Analyzer".
         Instead of just reading questions, the user inputs answers to see immediate visual feedback.
         - Top: Introduction and Context.
         - Left Column: Inputs for Demographics (Sec 1) and Strategic Drivers (Sec 4).
         - Right Column: Service Demand Matrix (Sec 2&3) linked to a Bar Chart, and Factor Analysis linked to a Radar Chart.
         - Logic: All inputs trigger real-time updates to the visualizations.
    -->

